<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>128</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs pi Okchalinchi ya̱,
 Hatak ilbʋsha yʋt
 Im anumpa e haklo cha,
 Hʋpi okcha̱yashke.

[V2]
 Ʋba isht taloa 'chukma,
 Hatak isunlʋsh ʋt
 Tahlepa sipokni kia,
 Isht e taloashke.

[V3]
 Pin Chisʋs pulla hatukmʋt
 Et pi pi̱sa hokʋt,
 Auet pi̱ hulla hi oka,
 Il ahni pullashke.

[V4]
 Pi chu̱kʋsh okpulo chatuk;
 Hatak nan ashʋchi,
 Chisʋs im issish fehna kʋt
 Pi hlakoffichashke.

[V5]
 Chihowa pi̱ Shaiyahli ma!
 Chisʋs pulla kak o̱,
 Auet ish pi̱ nukha̱klo cha,
 Ish pi apelashke.

[V6]
 Chisʋs chi hohchihi̱fo ka,
 Pi chu̱kʋsh atukma
 Nuktalali achukma he,
 Pit e chi hoyoshke.</lyrics>
<title>Chisʋs pi Okchalinchi ya ƲIT128</title>
</song>